data.description: Cape Coral's Most Popular Floor Plan, BETTER THAN NEW! This is the Cali, with 4 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, and over 1800 sq. ft. of living space. This home has utilities in and ALL ASSESSMENTS PAID. This property is NOT LOCATED in a FLOOD ZONE.  We have added a 600 sq. ft. plus pool deck with a Beautiful Saltwater Pool featuring a Sun Shelf, Bubblers, and Dynamic Lighting that turns Your backyard into an Outdoor Oasis. We have added an Extended Pan-roof for Poolside Shade to further your enjoyment. The Back and Side Yard is Fenced In with a 6' White Privacy Fence, perfect for your pets. Additional Upgrades; 1. They have extended the Home Warranty good until July of 2027. 2. Full House Generator Hookup, plug in your generator and you're set in any emergency. 3. Surge Protection throughout Your home. 4. Water Filtration System. 5. Smart Home Upgrades, and ADT Security System. 6. Ladder Access to the Attic with built-in Storage and Shelving. 7. A Garbage/Recycle Cabinet and a storage/organization cabinet in the kitchen.8. Underground Utilities! Move In Ready and with this home, you can enjoy Florida Living at its finest right from the closing table!
